---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About Us — Deskbly" description="Learn more about Deskbly and our mission to help you find the best home office gear." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="page-header">
				<h1>About Deskbly</h1>
				<p>Helping you build the perfect home office, one honest review at a time.</p>
			</section>

			<div class="about-content">
				<div class="about-section">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>
					<p>
						Deskbly started because we were tired of the same old "review" sites. 
						You know the ones — they list 20 products with rewritten Amazon descriptions, 
						call it a "best of" list, and slap affiliate links everywhere.
					</p>
					<p>
						We wanted something different. Real reviews from people who actually use the products. 
						Honest opinions that don't shy away from pointing out flaws. And most importantly — 
						recommendations you can trust.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="about-section">
					<h2>Who We Are</h2>
					<p>
						We're a team of remote workers, home office enthusiasts, and product reviewers 
						who spend way too much time researching desks, chairs, and accessories.
					</p>
					<p>
						We've worked from home for years — some of us in tiny apartments, others in 
						dedicated home offices. We've bought too many chairs, built too many desks, 
						and learned from too many mistakes.
					</p>
					<p>
						Now we share what we've learned so you don't have to make the same mistakes.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="about-section">
					<h2>What We Do</h2>
					<p>At Deskbly, we:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Research thoroughly</strong> — We spend hours comparing specs, reading user reviews, and testing products ourselves</li>
						<li><strong>Give honest opinions</strong> — If a product is garbage, we say so — even if it means we don't earn a commission</li>
						<li><strong>Focus on value</strong> — We believe the best product isn't always the most expensive</li>
						<li><strong>Keep it real</strong> — No sponsored posts, no paid reviews, no fluff</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="about-section">
					<h2>Our Promise to You</h2>
					<p>
						Here's what you can always expect from Deskbly:
					</p>
					<div class="promise-grid">
						<div class="promise-item">
							<span class="promise-icon">🔍</span>
							<h3>Honest Reviews</h3>
							<p>We tell you what's good and what's not. No fluff, no filler.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="promise-item">
							<span class="promise-icon">💰</span>
							<h3>Value First</h3>
							<p>We recommend products at every price point — not just the expensive ones.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="promise-item">
							<span class="promise-icon">🤝</span>
							<h3>Transparency</h3>
							<p>Some links are affiliate links. We explain this clearly. It never affects our recommendations.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="promise-item">
							<span class="promise-icon">🎯</span>
							<h3>Your Best Interest</h3>
							<p>If we wouldn't buy it, we won't recommend it. Simple as that.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="about-section">
					<h2>How We Make Money</h2>
					<p>
						Deskbly is supported by affiliate commissions. When you click a product link and make a purchase, 
						we may earn a small commission — at no extra cost to you.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Here's our promise:</strong> Affiliate commissions <em>never</em> influence our recommendations. 
						If a product is terrible, we won't recommend it — even if it pays well. We'd rather lose a 
						commission than lose your trust.
					</p>
					<p>
						We're transparent about this because we believe you deserve to know how we operate.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="about-section">
					<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
					<p>
						Have questions? Want to work together? Found an error in our reviews?
						We'd love to hear from you.
					</p>
					<p>
						📧 <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@deskbly.com">hello@deskbly.com</a>
					</p>
					<p>
						We typically respond within 24-48 hours.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="about-section cta-section">
					<h2>Ready to Build Your Perfect Setup?</h2>
					<p>Check out our latest reviews and buying guides.</p>
					<div class="cta-buttons">
						<a href="/blog" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Reviews</a>
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Us</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.about-section {
		background: white;
		padding: 2em;
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	.about-section h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: #0f172a;
	}
	.about-section p {
		color: #64748b;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
	.about-section ul {
		color: #64748b;
		line-height: 1.8;
		padding-left: 1.2em;
	}
	.about-section li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	.about-section a {
		color: #38bdf8;
	}
	.promise-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5em;
		margin-top: 1.5em;
	}
	.promise-item {
		background: #f8fafc;
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}
	.promise-icon {
		font-size: 2em;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
	}
	.promise-item h3 {
		font-size: 1em;
		margin: 0 0 0.3em 0;
		color: #0f172a;
	}
	.promise-item p {
		font-size: 0.9em;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
		color: white;
	}
	.cta-section h2 {
		color: white;
	}
	.cta-section p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1em;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	.btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		padding: 0.8em 1.8em;
		border-radius: 10px;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}
	.btn-primary {
		background: #38bdf8;
		color: #0f172a !important;
	}
	.btn-primary:hover {
		background: #7dd3fc;
	}
	.btn-outline {
		background: transparent;
		color: white !important;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
	}
	.btn-outline:hover {
		border-color: white;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}
	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.promise-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
